{"tid":1561900,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Hosting / VPS 推介… ?","createTime":"2019-09-11T19:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T13:54:09.000Z","uid":316066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0a9a9f37837deacb8f591d72962f2d741a5cca","tid":1561900,"uid":316066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:09:43.000Z","msg":"話說小弟其實一直用開 OVH 個 VPS, 價錢同性能方面真係抵屌到爆，仲有 Free DDOS Protection .<br />\n<br />\n1 Core<br />\n2 GB Ram<br />\n20 GB SSD<br />\n<br />\n都係講緊 28 蚊港幣一個月<br />\n下載速度我用 WiFi 下載平均都有 5Mb/s (倫敦server)<br />\n<br />\n講真我真係唔係好想轉，但係佢最近轉咗新 system，搞到好似AWS 咁，呢個都唔係重點，重點係我張卡比佢個 system ban 咗... （應該係之前第二個 account 有自動續期，佢自動 renew 咗但係我冇找數...）<br />\n<br />\n所以依家諗住順便睇吓有冇啲咩 Hosting / VPS 本身 Located 響香港，順便等個 Ping 低啲。<br />\n<br />\n有無咩性價比高嘅可以介紹嚟試下？（利申：唔用 AWS, Google 同埋 Azure)"},{"pid":"4c39f7704228bf2f68e141d2b8f338157e7c9540","tid":1561900,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3c40b2d0a894518db6ecf9f254aa76955937420","tid":1561900,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:10:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0907e4b1297aa8ca9e4d147137fe9dc5a8f99a8d","tid":1561900,"uid":126394,"like